de.dimensionv.android.widget.dashboardlayout

Interface DashboardItemContent


  • public interface DashboardItemContent

    This interface should be used for all content-objects passed to the ContainerDashboardItem.

    If a content-object implements this interface, it can be used to automatically feed the information necessary to create a DashboardItem.

    Since:
    API 1.0.0
